productBaseInfoV1.title: MICHAEL KORS Access Dylan (For Men) Smartwatch(Black Strap, Regular)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: With a sleek profile and many impressive features, the Michael Kors Access Dylan smartwatch offers a beautiful combination of style and technology. Since it is powered by Android Wear, you can use it with a wide range of Android devices. Not only that, it is also compatible with iOS devices. Featuring multiple touchscreen watch faces, this smartwatch lets you customize its dial depending on your mood and style. Apart from that, it also features activity tracking, voice control, notification alerts, Smart Help from Google and a silicone strap. Since it is water-resistant, you can wear it anywhere you like. Additional Details: This devices requires the Michael Kors Access app or the Android Wear app. The battery life averages up to 2 days with typical use and it recharges from 10% to 80% in about 2 hours.
